	<h3>Batchelor of Arts in Radio&mdash;Television</h3>
	<p>The radio-television major is designed to provide students with the skills and knowledge leading to careers in the field broadly defined as radio-television. Aside from broadcast stations, this major prepares students for jobs in cable television, production facilities and corporate and digital media.</p>
