		<h4>Broadcast Journalism</h4>
		<p>This track is designed for students who desire to work in broadcast as opposed to print (newspaper or magazine) journalism. Students wanting to be radio or TV news reporters, photographers, anchors or broadcast sports journalists should pick this track. </p>
