		<p>This track is designed for students who wish to employ electronic or digital media equipment to communicate messages. Either audio or video production may be emphasized. Students should pick this major if they want to be producers/directors, videographers, editors, or other audio/video recording specializations.  This track directly involves training and competency in the use of broadcast studio and field production equipment.</p>
	</div>
